# gptokeyb: 手柄 → 键盘。方向键导航, A/回车确定, B/ESC 退出。
# 用来验证 gptokeyb→love.keypressed 这条(将来 stage-1 要走的)路。
a = enter
b = esc
x = esc
y = esc
start = enter
back = esc
guide = esc

up = up
down = down
left = left
right = right

left_analog_up = up
left_analog_down = down
left_analog_left = left
left_analog_right = right
